WEBVTT

00:04.156 --> 00:06.324
[Medieval European music
playing]

00:12.898 --> 00:15.734
[Finger cymbals clicking]

00:19.505 --> 00:21.339
Ooh!

00:21.407 --> 00:22.340
[Applause]

00:22.408 --> 00:23.508
[Gasps]

00:23.576 --> 00:25.577
Hmm? Huh? Huh?

00:25.644 --> 00:28.980
I still don't get why some people
insist on dressing like pirates

00:29.048 --> 00:30.315
at a faire for knights.

00:30.383 --> 00:31.516
Because knights are boring.

00:31.584 --> 00:34.252
They're so, "milord this"
and "milady that."

00:34.320 --> 00:36.821
"Joust me!
Ooh, I've got the pox!"

00:36.889 --> 00:39.224
Pirates, on the other hand,
are awesome.

00:39.291 --> 00:40.625
Yarr!

00:42.661 --> 00:44.662
I got to fix this thing.

00:48.167 --> 00:50.168
[Grunting]

00:50.236 --> 00:52.137
Hmm? Huh?

00:52.204 --> 00:53.471
[Grunting and chuckling]

00:53.539 --> 00:54.906
Hello?
[gasps]

00:54.974 --> 00:57.142
Hmm.

00:57.209 --> 00:59.644
- [Laughing]
- [Screaming]

01:01.614 --> 01:04.114
I could knit a sash
in the time you're taking.

01:04.183 --> 01:06.117
[Gasps] [Growls]

01:06.185 --> 01:07.485
[Laughs]

01:07.553 --> 01:09.554
[Screams]

01:11.000 --> 01:17.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

